interpretation_guide.p_win: Probability that price closes on the same side of open as current position (leader wins)
interpretation_guide.ev_pct: Expected value per trade as percentage of position size
interpretation_guide.kelly: Optimal bet size as percentage of bankroll (MAX = 100% win rate)
interpretation_guide.samples: Number of data points observed (higher = more statistically reliable)
interpretation_guide.trade_opportunities: Unique windows that hit this bucket (actual tradeable setups)
interpretation_guide.recency: How recent the trades were (100% = all recent, 50% = avg age equals half-life, lower = older)
interpretation_guide.composite_score: Combined score ranking opportunities by return potential, confidence, and recency
